	* glade/zapping.glade: [<<][<][>][>>]
	* src/ttxview.c: Added bookmarks. They cannot be removed yet (edit
	by hand zapping.conf)
	* src/zmisc.c: Got rid of redundant malloc, free's, it should
	be faster now.

